5:
...All right, that should be everyone in
this area taken care of.
8:
Thanks for helping me out, guys. You
really bailed me out of a tight spot!
12:
Just glad we were able to lend a
hand.
15:
...The storm caused a ton of
damage, huh? It's a good thing
nobody died, but...
19:
Don't you worry. The Fellowship of
Floof is here to make sure everyone
gets back on their feet!
23:
We'll still need your help too, so keep
your spirits up!
27:
I've never been cheered up by being
told to work before...
30:
But you're right. No sense in letting
myself get all pessimistic.
47:
We finished treating all the patients
in the western section! They seem
like they're going to heal up just fine.
51:
...That's good. I should hurry up and
finish my own work as well.
56:
S-sorry, just dizzy for a moment. I'll
be fine.
60:
You seem tired. Maybe you should
take a breakâ€”
63:
There's no time for a break when I
have patients waiting for me.
65:
I'll do what I'm here to do. You
should too.
83:
O-of course the patients take
priority! She wasn't wrong there.
86:
But she didn't look happy at all even
though everyone's doing fine.
90: That's just... not good for anyone!
95:
In that case, you know how to help,
don't you?
103: And I'm gonna need your assistance!
107:
Pythica? Don't mind me. You can
keep speaking with your patients...
111:
Oh, actually, I wanted to let you
know that we took care of everyone
in the northern section!
114:
You did? I was just about to head
over there myself...
117:
Ehehe, it was no problem with Alk
and Stella backing me up!
120: But, uh... I wanted to give this to you!
123: Is this... an aroma oil? It smells good...
126:
Apparently it helps with getting
good sleep! The brand advertises
itself as "self-indulgence to bring
world peace" or something like that!
129:
It's a souvenir I've been meaning to
give you, but I never found the right
timing...
133:
The point is, you should rest more! I'll
handle more of the work so you can
have time to relax!
136:
It's the least I can do since you've
watched over me from the
beginning!
140:
Ah, I need to report to the vice
captain! Excuse me!
145:
Thank you for looking after me. I'm
sorry I let myself get to this point.
146:
...I'll be counting on you. Can I leave
the rest in your capable hands?
154:
Thank you so, so much for all your
hard work! Everyone's healed up
now!
163:
I'm glad your nurse friend is doing
better now too.
167:
Ehehe, she said the aroma oil
worked wonders! She's been
sleeping like a baby at night!
171:
You know, you look refreshed
yourself.
176:
That's because... I'm so happy that
she's counting on me!
179:
But I wouldn't have gotten this far
without your help! I'm seriously in
your debt!
183:
If you ask me... the majority of credit
lies with you.
188:
You've been an amazing nurse since
the start.
192:
Ehehe, you think so? You guys are
such good flatterers.
195:
But don't think I'm done yet. I'll keep
working on myself and my skills...
199:
So whenever anyone's in need of a
helping hand, I'll be there to make
them happy and healthy again!
